EObjectAttributeValueFilter

public EObjectAttributeValueFilter(EAttribute attribute,
                                   java.lang.Object attributeValue)
Filter EObjects on the value of an attribute.

Filter EObject instances whose type is EAttribute#getContainerEClass(), and whose link EObject#eGet(org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature) value is Object.equals(Object) equal to the filter value.

Parameters:
attribute - an EMF attribute (cannot be null).
attributeValue - the expected value of the EMF attribute (may be null).
